kdna-web-server is a server-side adapter layer for the KDNA runtime.
It wraps @aikdna/kdna-core and @aikdna/kdna-studio-core for use in
Node.js, Next.js, and Express environments.

All KDNA decryption, license verification, and entitlement checks
are performed server-side. The browser receives only metadata and
load-plan state — never keying material or decrypted payloads.

